#

Creamy Shrimp Garlic Soup

30 min
$15
400 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

ShellfishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeNut-Free

Cuisine:

AmericanSeafoodComfort Food

Course:

Main CourseAppetizer

Tags:

SoupSeafoodComfort Food

Description

A rich and velvety soup packed with delectable shrimp and a hint of garlic, perfect for a cozy dinner.

Ingredients

  • shrimp, peeled and deveined: 1 lb
  • garlic, minced: 4 cloves
  • onion, chopped: 1 medium
  • chicken broth: 4 cups
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • parsley, chopped (for garnish): 2 tablespoons
